title: 4mm Insulated Banana Plugs Yellow
blurb:
These are quality 4mm banana plugs and are perfect for test equipment. They have side cable entry, solder termination and meaty finger grips on the side. The piggyback design allows for another banana plug to be inserted in the rear and being fully insulated, they're ideal where OH&S and safety are a concern.
* Rated for 85°C
